Package: longworkR
Title: Longitudinal Employment Analytics for vecshift Data
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Giampaolo", "Montaletti", , "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122"))
Description: Analytics and visualization tools for longitudinal employment data
    processed by the vecshift package. Includes survival analysis, impact evaluation,
    difference-in-differences, network analysis, and advanced visualization capabilities
    for employment transitions and career trajectories. Features comprehensive data
    protection with synthetic data generation for public distribution while maintaining
    privacy of real employment records.
